item.title: Holy week services
item.description: Dates, times and locations for holy week services Easter is around the corner, here are the dates, times and locations for Holy weeks services. Palm Sunday: 28th March St Augustine’s 8am and 5:30pm St Albans’s 10am Maundy Thursday: 1st April Combined Parish Service, St Albans 6pm Good Friday: 2nd April Combined Parish Service, St Augustine’s 8am Saturday Easter Eve: 3rd April Combined Parish Service, St Albans 6pm Sunday Easter Day 4th April Combined Parish Service, St Augustine’s 8am
